title: What Did Patriots Players Think Of Fan Turnout At Victory Parade? | New England Patriots Parade | NESN.com
text:
by NESN Staff on Wed, Feb 8, 2017 at 12:03AM 2,501 Tweet 
New England Patriots players loved the support they received from fans during the team’s Super Bowl LI victory parade Tuesday in Boston. 
NESN.com’s Michaela Vernava and Rachel Holt were there, and had a chance to talk with several Patriots, including Julian Edelman and Martellus Bennett, about the crazy day. 
Hear what the champs had to say in the video above. More Stories
